    "body": "Hi, based on discussion with Vitaly,\r\nthe goal is \r\n\r\n> The goal is this: when we start using the verification proxy, it can provide us with an additional layer of security, as calls to possibly untrusted eth providers like Infura can be verified with the verification proxy\r\n\r\nThe goal would be to add a toggle to be able to start configure the starting of the nimbus after a restart to account for RPC client configuration.\r\nI'll start with setting up the environment to be able to catch up on Vitaly's code and start the implemenation.\r\n\r\n\r\nUI render : \r\n\r\n![Screenshot from 2024-01-16 09-42-40](https://github.com/status-im/status-desktop/assets/2589171/ade1a971-ca32-4874-a57f-7caabed371a5)\r\n\r\n![Screenshot from 2024-01-16 09-43-05](https://github.com/status-im/status-desktop/assets/2589171/bc2283e6-1769-4af2-9214-eb35eb676543)\r\n",
